  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This a prospective study when the clinician decides to use sugammadex, heart rate will be
      recorded every minute for 15 minutes following its administration. If bradycardia occurs and
      a clinical decision is made to treat it, the medications and doses used will be recorded.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
